<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag 'profile.png', alt: 'profile image', class: 'profile-img' %>
        <h2>Skills and languages</h2>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
            </div>

          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8 about">
        <p>I am a father of four. I love puzzles and riddles because I like thinking logically and problem solving. I enjoy sports, gaming, and movies, and I'm passionate about theatre, music, writing, and cooking. I'm an eclipse chaser and I'll travel the world to see them.</p>
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>

          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controls="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block job">
              Hospitality/Management
              <p>Team management, leadership, customer service, workflow management</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card card-block job">
              Actor/Writer
              <p>Collaboration, creativity, problem solving, deadline management</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block job">
              Utah Valley University, BS Theatre Performance (2018, expected)
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>